<div id="modal_delete_node" class="modal hide" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
    <h3 id="myModalLabel">Delete node?</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>Are you sure you want to delete the "<strong><%= @node.label %></strong>" node from your project?</p>
    <p>When you delete a node, all of the following are deleted with it:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Notes</li>
      <li>Attachments</li>
      <li>Evidence</li>
      <li>Child nodes (and their children)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <%= link_to 'Delete', @node, :class => 'btn btn-danger', :method => :delete %>
    <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Close</button>
  </div>
</div>